      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical verified against NAFEMS LE1 and LE10 linear elastic benchmarks. Patch-test convergence confirmed for tetrahedral and hexahedral element libraries used in pedicle screw models. Results archived in FDA verification report VR-2023-001."
    },
    {
